title._content: Group of unidentified women and children in front of a farmhouse, ca. 1920

description._content: Creator: Unidentified Location: Queensland Description:A group of people posing in front of a country house. Two children and a woman are sitting in a buggy, while another woman is on horseback. A child is standing next to a goat and a dog is lying in the grass. A third woman is looking down from the veranda.
